<br>
There's ways to get to some tier 2 zones without killing a boss, yes, but beyond that, don't kid yourselves.  Even the guilds of lesser ability that may eventually work their way into teir 2 zones will not be getting much farther.  While I don't think everyone should get to see and do everything, I definitly see a big problem with how things are; 4 or 5 tiers, most people will only ever see 1 or 2.  And even if you ARE in a powerful guild, missing one single night can really trip you up unless you give out your info to a friend to get you flagged, it also forces guilds to have to do stuff multiples times just to get a few straglers flagged.<br>
<br>
It really was not a good idea to make the teir 3+ zones so hard to gain enterance to for non-ubers, I don't think everyone should see everything, but as it is the setup is pretty silly.<br>
